Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.49,0:04:29.48,ep,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,無 風 日
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.34,0:04:40.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有你的快遞
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.81,0:04:43.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哦 辛苦了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.20,0:04:46.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,給 請在這裡簽名
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.05,0:04:47.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.36,0:04:50.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(640,630)}那個 工作方面缺不缺人手呢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.90,0:04:53.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(640,640)}他說想找個工作
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.37,0:04:56.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(640,640)}哦 你就是大家說的那個宇宙少年嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.14,0:04:58.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(640,640)}找工作啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.54,0:05:00.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(640,640)}上個月正好有個人退休了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.33,0:05:01.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(640,640)}咦？那麼…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.90,0:05:04.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(640,640)}但是已經雇了新人
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.53,0:05:08.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(640,640)}沒事的沒事的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.81,0:05:10.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(640,640)}抓魚的活兒肯定找得到
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.78,0:05:13.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊？ 沒有呢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.73,0:05:14.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,瞧瞧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.66,0:05:18.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為錯過了洋流交匯帶 最近一直都是這樣
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.66,0:05:18.68,tips,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,註：暖流與寒流的交匯地帶往往漁業資源豐富
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.70,0:05:21.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等到忙起來的時候 我會找你的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.16,0:05:22.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.97,0:05:25.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你也看到了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.28,0:05:28.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我現在正忙著整理賬單
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.07,0:05:30.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這活外行也幹不了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.40,0:05:32.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,尋寶呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.77,0:05:34.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,地點倒是有了眉目
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.98,0:05:37.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是還要過三天才能到
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.93,0:05:38.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這樣啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.22,0:05:41.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抱歉 害你期待了半天
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.67,0:05:42.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒事
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.05,0:05:45.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我差不多該去送快遞了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.35,0:05:49.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼 我試著自己找看看
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.26,0:05:51.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.27,0:06:00.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很好 很好 很好 很好
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.91,0:06:02.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,稍微往上點 往上點
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.68,0:06:05.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,笨蛋 都說是最上面了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.08,0:06:08.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不對 左邊  那邊往左
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.15,0:06:38.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抱歉 做不來…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.19,0:06:51.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,工作的適用條件居然如此嚴格
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.18,0:06:54.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Chamber 數據庫有更新嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.59,0:06:57.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,仍未找到適合貴官從事的工作
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.77,0:07:02.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼情況？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.70,0:07:05.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,艦團的推進裝置正在逐一停止
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.60,0:07:24.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼回事？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.09,0:07:25.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喲
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.98,0:07:27.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,皮尼歐
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.65,0:07:30.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別在那裡傻站著
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.31,0:07:31.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,轉換一下心情吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.50,0:07:34.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,皮尼歐 艦團停下了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.94,0:07:35.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,發生了什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.37,0:07:37.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒風了啦 沒風
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.41,0:07:40.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,行了 集合了 跟我來
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.59,0:07:45.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這肉夠大吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.33,0:07:47.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,足夠大吃一頓了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.06,0:07:49.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真虧你搞得到手啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.73,0:07:50.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好期待
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.14,0:07:53.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過現在搞派對沒關係嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.59,0:07:57.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好不容易碰到無風日 應該有很多修理工作要做吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.96,0:08:01.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,混到我這個位置 手下幹活的人要多少有多少
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.40,0:08:03.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.30,0:08:05.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,首先是弗蘭基的船
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.81,0:08:06.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.04,0:08:08.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,電源關掉了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.63,0:08:09.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 我已經確認過了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.12,0:08:12.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,走吧 派對會場在那邊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.73,0:08:16.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂 剛剛那是皮尼歐的工作吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.97,0:08:18.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.49,0:08:21.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是怎麼回事
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.96,0:08:25.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哦 因為無風日風平浪靜
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.61,0:08:28.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以會選在這樣的日子裡維修船舶
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.35,0:08:31.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,艦團會離開銀河道
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.49,0:08:32.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,電力也會中斷
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.83,0:08:34.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以只有維修人員才能工作
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.30,0:08:36.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,其他人則全都放假
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.66,0:08:39.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是 這樣啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.33,0:08:41.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,貝貝爾 你還好吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.56,0:08:42.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.37,0:08:48.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,風景不賴吧 這可是絕佳位置
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.65,0:08:51.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好漂亮
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.46,0:08:55.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雷德 無風的海面就是這樣的哦
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.94,0:09:01.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,紗雅 梅露蒂
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.27,0:09:03.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你們好慢
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.35,0:09:04.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快過來
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.59,0:09:21.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 那裡好像不錯呢
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.36,0:09:23.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要游泳嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.31,0:09:24.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,贊成！
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.14,0:09:32.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雷德也來嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.27,0:09:33.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.95,0:09:34.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很舒服的哦
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.35,0:09:37.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別穿那件老土的衣服了啦
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.71,0:09:38.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我脫
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.63,0:09:46.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 身材挺棒嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.05,0:10:00.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,呀 好熱啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.17,0:10:02.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,奧爾德姆醫生
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.78,0:10:03.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我就打擾一下了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.15,0:10:04.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.57,0:10:10.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,終於要開始了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.46,0:10:14.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這可是費了好大勁才搞到的好肉
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.97,0:10:16.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很好吃的哦
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.95,0:10:26.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,電力還沒恢復啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.30,0:10:29.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂 破廢鐵 你不能想點辦法嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.05,0:10:31.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,烤就行了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.09,0:10:32.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒錯沒錯
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.20,0:10:44.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對象焚化完畢
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.67,0:10:47.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你搞啥啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.43,0:10:52.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是的…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.93,0:10:57.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 糟糕了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.82,0:10:58.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒有那個
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.30,0:10:59.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼了？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.67,0:11:01.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.91,0:11:02.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂 雷德
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.41,0:11:08.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我有件事要交給你去辦
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.09,0:11:09.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是工作？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.16,0:11:10.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒錯
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.58,0:11:13.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,去鐵匠婆婆那裡一趟
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.76,0:11:14.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,由你去最合適
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.97,0:11:17.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不 這是只有你才能做到的工作
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.81,0:11:20.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等等 你要讓雷德到那種地方去嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.42,0:11:24.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那當然 誰讓他浪費掉了一盤子的肉
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.79,0:11:26.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,交給你了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.89,0:11:48.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,接下來是背後
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.89,0:11:50.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雷德他不要緊吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.11,0:11:55.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那裡好癢
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.93,0:11:56.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(640,630)}果然癢吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.27,0:11:58.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(640,640)}真是的…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.14,0:12:02.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(640,640)}這下吃完烤肉又要發胖了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.85,0:12:06.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(640,640)}什麼「又要」啊 梅露蒂你根本不用擔心吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.65,0:12:08.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(640,640)}每個人都有自己的標準嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.06,0:12:09.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(640,640)}是吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.12,0:12:11.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(640,640)}我完全不在意
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.84,0:12:14.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(640,640)}也有不少男生喜歡肉感的女生嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.91,0:12:16.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(640,640)}你還真是天真啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.19,0:12:21.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,誤會這點的話可是要吃苦頭的哦
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.50,0:12:25.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還 還是應該運動一下吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.06,0:12:27.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是 是呢…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.01,0:12:29.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是莉吉特
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.23,0:12:30.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,艾米在嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.37,0:12:33.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.51,0:12:36.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,起重機塔的噴水器你知道吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.21,0:12:39.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雖然電力恢復了 那東西卻沒動靜
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.77,0:12:40.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,誒 又壞了？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.56,0:12:44.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你能用衝浪風箏上去開啟水泵嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.56,0:12:44.40,ruby,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(558,650)}Surf Kite
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.87,0:12:47.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,誒 我接下來要參加烤肉派對的…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.76,0:12:48.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.65,0:12:49.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好的 我知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.13,0:12:51.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,烤肉？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.09,0:12:54.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒事 那麼拜託你了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.18,0:12:58.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,來比試一場吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.47,0:13:01.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,ok 我可不會輸給你
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.40,0:13:03.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這樣一來就不用擔心發胖了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.30,0:13:07.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為何在積極攝取食物的同時
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.13,0:13:10.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,又執著於維持體型
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.53,0:13:12.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這就是所謂的少女心啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.54,0:13:15.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,本機無法理解
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.51,0:13:16.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那倒也是
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.75,0:13:19.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過 要怎麼辦呢
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.36,0:13:25.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,…破廢鐵 你很黑嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.95,0:13:39.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是這裡嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.95,0:13:41.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊呀 小弟弟你一個人？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.33,0:13:47.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這臉蛋長得真甜啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.70,0:13:51.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 好嫩的身體
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.99,0:13:52.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼什麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.86,0:14:02.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,終點是起重機塔的頂端
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.35,0:14:04.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.97,0:14:08.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,準備
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.24,0:14:12.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,開始
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.22,0:14:27.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂 升空的方法不要那麼亂來
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.30,0:14:30.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,詢問採取該行動的必要性
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.30,0:14:30.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別動
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.49,0:14:33.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,皮尼歐
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.10,0:14:37.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我船上的絞盤你還修不修了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.17,0:14:38.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,會修的啦
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.05,0:14:41.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你不是工作忙得很嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.74,0:14:43.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要在意這些小事嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.76,0:14:46.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你也一起吃吧 馬上就要開始了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.13,0:14:52.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等等 別跑啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.12,0:14:55.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在我們這裡工作怎麼樣
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.40,0:14:58.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Chamber Chamber
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.27,0:15:00.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,少尉發生了緊急情況
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.47,0:15:02.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,都叫你別動了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.84,0:15:05.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這對那傢伙來說也算是有意義的社會實踐
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.50,0:15:07.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,本機表示同意
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.73,0:15:11.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,皮尼歐 你在那做什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.74,0:15:12.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你誰啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.60,0:15:16.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,莉吉特
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.82,0:15:18.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你怎麼這身打扮
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.90,0:15:21.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我剛剛在監督船底的檢修
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.82,0:15:22.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哦 這樣啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.51,0:15:25.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我說 這裡的電力什麼時候才會恢復啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.70,0:15:29.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,工作沒法按時完成 可能要停到傍晚了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.74,0:15:31.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,休息一下吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.86,0:15:33.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還沒開始嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.81,0:15:36.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這樣啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.07,0:15:37.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,打擾了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.25,0:15:39.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,誒
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.38,0:15:41.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼了？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.63,0:15:42.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 不…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.10,0:15:45.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你這身泳衣好大膽呢
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.77,0:15:47.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,誒 是嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.98,0:15:53.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,新人不用承擔業績指標的啦
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.21,0:15:55.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等一下嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.86,0:15:57.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到底怎麼回事 我到底做了什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.65,0:15:59.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,第一歸我了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.82,0:16:00.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還沒結束呢
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.92,0:16:01.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我才不會輸
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.15,0:16:07.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你肯定能成為我們店的頭牌
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.09,0:16:13.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 臀部曲線也很完美
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.68,0:16:14.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好有活力
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.01,0:16:16.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,體力也很棒
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.85,0:16:23.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,艾米
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.92,0:16:24.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.43,0:16:27.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 總是艾米佔甜頭
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.52,0:16:28.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是比賽就是比賽
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.86,0:16:30.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 等一下
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.19,0:16:35.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抓緊了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.48,0:16:46.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,誒？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.94,0:16:47.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,糟了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.03,0:16:51.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,成功了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.21,0:16:53.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,第一名歸我了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.84,0:17:13.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好 這樣就行了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.59,0:17:15.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,剛剛好險呢
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.23,0:17:18.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,話說回來 你怎麼會在那裡
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.83,0:17:20.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也不知道
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.18,0:17:24.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,總之辛苦了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.63,0:17:29.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,來了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.21,0:17:30.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看好了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.20,0:18:02.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼 我接著工作去了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.20,0:18:10.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼回事？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.78,0:18:13.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,順著這條路走就行了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.66,0:18:34.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是這裡
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.54,0:18:39.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是場不錯的運動
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.86,0:18:40.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.81,0:18:43.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這樣一來就可以放開大吃了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.90,0:18:45.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,詢問採取該行動的必要性
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.15,0:18:48.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,重複 詢問採取該行動的必要性…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.82,0:18:48.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我說了不要動
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.25,0:18:57.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,差不多可以了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.76,0:19:03.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這個
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.37,0:19:12.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,年輕人 你想要這個做什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.80,0:19:17.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,算了 拿去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.57,0:19:20.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果這樣就能解決的話
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.86,0:19:21.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請問…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.75,0:19:32.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是某種零件嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.20,0:19:38.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,又要回到那裡去嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.35,0:19:49.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這 是…？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.82,0:20:03.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可惡 誰幹的好事
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.01,0:20:05.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,居然把派對的事到處提
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.92,0:20:08.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,歡迎回來
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.01,0:20:11.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,辛苦了 宇宙少年
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.81,0:20:14.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只有鹽總覺得不夠味呢
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.85,0:20:15.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虧你趕上了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.41,0:20:18.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好 誰想要？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.95,0:20:28.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,果然婆婆的醬汁最棒了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.74,0:20:30.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雷德 不快吃就沒了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.16,0:20:33.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,給
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.37,0:20:39.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好吃嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.60,0:20:44.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也嚐嚐自己勞動的結晶吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.72,0:20:46.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,給
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.49,0:20:50.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這 這是…？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.80,0:21:07.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 起風了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.00,0:21:10.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好了 幹活去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.70,0:21:12.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吃飽了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.16,0:21:14.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 大概
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.90,0:21:17.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這樣啊 畢竟你是途中才來的嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.13,0:21:20.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抱歉 這場派對明明是為你準備的
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.79,0:21:23.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,誒 你沒聽說嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.11,0:21:25.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為雷德一直沒有找到工作
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.30,0:21:28.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,皮尼歐為了替你打氣才特意安排的
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.45,0:21:30.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是 這樣嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.53,0:21:34.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,謝謝你為大家努力工作
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.66,0:21:38.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我 為大家…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:38.31,0:21:38.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒錯
Dialogue: 0,0:21:39.49,0:21:42.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,多虧有你 大家才吃到了美味的烤肉
Dialogue: 0,0:21:44.70,0:21:45.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,來 走吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:45.81,0:21:47.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我還會陪你一起去找工作的
Dialogue: 0,0:21:48.39,0:21:49.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不知道雷德哥哥適合什麼工作呢
Dialogue: 0,0:21:50.54,0:21:52.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,應該還是體力活吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:52.81,0:21:53.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,牛…不行
Dialogue: 0,0:21:54.28,0:21:54.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:21:56.40,0:21:57.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 皮尼歐
Dialogue: 0,0:21:57.97,0:21:59.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原來你在這種地方偷懶嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:21:59.85,0:22:02.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這 這可是名正言順的工…
Dialogue: 0,0:22:02.97,0:22:03.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對不起
Dialogue: 0,0:22:05.83,0:22:07.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,詢問採取該行動的必要性
Dialogue: 0,0:22:08.57,0:22:10.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,重複 詢問採取該行…
